title.rendered: Key Members from Alfa LU-VE visit TTE’s Head Office

content.rendered: TTE welcomed Andrea Paltrinieri, General Manager, LU-VE Middle East DMCC and Biju Thomas, Area Sales Manager – MEA from the LU-VE Group to their Head Office. Dilip Sharma, Executive Vice President, Roshan Samuel, Associate Vice President, Products & Solutions and Praveen Meledath, Assistant Manager – Sales & Estimation from the Products & Solutions division of TTE met with the key members. Alfa LU-VE (of LU-VE Group) is known worldwide for their innovative and futuristic refrigeration and air conditioning products. Together with TTE, they bring to the region a series of Air Coolers, Condensers and Blast Freezers.
